     <div class="grid-clear"></div>
    <div class="grid-span-4">
        <h2>My Role and Contribution</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-span-8 maxcharacterlength--54">
        <p>My key responsibilities were:</p>
        <ul>   
        <li>Conducted extensive user research at various construction sites.</li>
        <li>Designed user interfaces for both the iPad application and the web application, focusing on usability in challenging site conditions.</li>
        <li>Managed stakeholder communications, ensuring the project aligned with user needs and business objectives.</li> 
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-clear rowmargin--medium"></div>
