        <div>
            <h2>The Solution</h2>
            <p>Highlights of the platform:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>iPad Application: Designed for use with gloves, featuring Bluetooth connectivity for measurement tools and with that reducing neccessary interaction.</li>
                <li>Architect's Tool: An web-based application for uploading plans, planning routes, and streamlining feedback between architects and construction teams.</li>
            </ul>  
